[normal] I had to go on many training courses and follow a very circuitous route.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] The village Hall has been erected for two years, thank God.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] At the same time as I worked for the village Hall I learned from the community that there is a gr
[normal]eat need for a community bus. 
